[[Captain/Legends|Captain]] '''Fessix''' was in command of the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] [[Discord (Star Destroyer)|''Discord'']] in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]. He had a close relationship with [[Tyanna Tymb]] who provided him with information about her [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] customers.

